These volunteers provide quick pep talks near the coffee station, while a startup founder invites students to participate in a lunchtime pitch session. A cybersecurity company is engaging attendees with an interactive password cracking challenge on a laptop. Consulting firms are arranging glossy case study booklets on high tables, and workshops on networking etiquette are scheduled to commence in an adjoining classroom. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and the dean stops by to thank recruiters for their support of the university.

Alumni volunteers are sharing quick pep talks near the coffee station while assisting with preparations by stacking collapsed booths and gathering leftover brochures. A startup founder invites students to participate in a lunchtime pitch session. A cybersecurity company is conducting a password cracking challenge on a laptop, adding an interactive element to the event. Consulting firms are arranging glossy case study booklets on high tables, and workshops on networking etiquette are beginning in the adjoining classroom. The dean is visiting to thank recruiters for their support.

Alumni volunteers assist with preparations by stacking collapsed booths, gathering leftover brochures, and providing quick pep talks near the coffee station. A startup founder invites students to participate in a lunchtime pitch session, while a cybersecurity company engages attendees with an interactive password cracking challenge on a laptop. Consulting firms organize glossy case study booklets on high tables, and workshops on networking etiquette are scheduled to begin in an adjoining classroom. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and the dean stops by to thank recruiters for their support. Additionally, camera crews from the university media team are capturing interviews.

They also provide quick pep talks near the coffee station. A startup founder invites students to participate in a lunchtime pitch session, while a cybersecurity company engages attendees with an interactive password cracking challenge on a laptop. Consulting firms arrange glossy case study booklets on high tables, and workshops on networking etiquette are scheduled to commence in an adjoining classroom. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and the dean visits to thank recruiters for their support of the university. Camera crews from the media team capture interviews throughout the fair.

Inside, alumni volunteers assist with preparations by stacking collapsed booths and gathering leftover brochures while providing quick pep talks near the coffee station. A startup founder invites students to participate in a lunchtime pitch session, and a cybersecurity company engages attendees with an interactive password cracking challenge on a laptop. Consulting firms arrange glossy case study booklets on high tables, and workshops on networking etiquette are scheduled to commence in an adjoining classroom. Recruiters remind students to follow up with personalized emails, and the dean visits to thank recruiters for their support. Additionally, camera crews from the university media team capture interviews throughout the preparations.
